    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine retains its factory individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis is sharpened with Bilstein dampers, while the M-Variable differential provides exceptional mechanical grip through the corners. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, but the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a mechanically sound example ready for the B-roads.",
